How to use?
just Define the beans with name and class like normal and put @Autowire Annotation above the following to perform the injection

Ways to inject Using @Autowire
1)  Above property/ Variable
2)  above Setter Method
3)   Above Constructor


how it works?
it will inject the bean / Object according to the Autowire Annotation position  like above




problem?
if Single Bean which is to be Injected is Present then it will Work perfect but it Multiple bean in XML file with same type then it will throw Exception
[ Exception - Expected Single Found multiple]

it works on byType logic



Solution ?

to solve this we use @Qualifier("bean name which is to be injected") ;
it Solve the Problem Of multiple bean of same Type
just provide the @Qualifier("name of bean which you want to inject")
